```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start[Resource Loader<br/>DefaultResourceLoader.reload] --> Resolve{PackageManager.resolve}
    Resolve --> PkgPkg[Package Resources<br/>extensions, skills,<br/>prompts, themes]
    PkgPkg --> GetEnabled{getEnabledResources<br/>Filter by settings}
    
    GetEnabled --> EnvExt[Enabled Extensions Paths]
    GetEnabled --> EnvSkills[Enabled Skills Paths]
    GetEnabled --> EnvPrompts[Enabled Prompts Paths]
    GetEnabled --> EnvThemes[Enabled Themes Paths]
    
    EnvExt --> LoadExt[loadExtensions<br/>via jiti]
    EnvSkills --> LoadSkills[loadSkills]
    EnvPrompts --> LoadPrompts[loadPromptTemplates]
    EnvThemes --> LoadThemes[loadThemes]
    
    LoadExt --> Runtime[Extension Runtime]
    LoadSkills --> Skills[Skills Array]
    LoadPrompts --> Prompts[PromptTemplates]
    LoadThemes --> Themes[Themes]
    
    Runtime --> Ctx[Context Files<br/>AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md]
    Ctx --> SysPrompt[System Prompt<br/>default/override/append]
    
    SysPrompt --> Done[Resources Ready]
    Skills --> Done
    Prompts --> Done
    Themes --> Done
```

---

**Explanation**:
1. **Resolve**: PackageManager lấy resources từ installed packages.
2. **Filter**: Lọc enabled resources dựa trên settings (`extensions.enabled`, `skills.disabled`, etc.).
3. **Load**: Từng loại resource được load (extensions via jiti, skills/prompts/themes từ filesystem/package paths).
4. **Context files**: Đã load sớm (trong `reload()` constructor? Actually `loadProjectContextFiles` gọi trong constructor, và `reload()` không gọi lại? Cần check: `DefaultResourceLoader` lưu `agentsFiles` và không reload chúng? Code cho thấy `loadProjectContextFiles` được gọi trong constructor; `reload()` không reload context files, chỉ reload extensions/skills/prompts/themes. Vậy context files chỉ load startup.
5. **System prompt**: combine default, override, append.
6. **Ready**: ResourceLoader now provides `getExtensions()`, `getSkills()`, etc.
